# long messages




# Initial and long messages og the bot
MESSAGE1="Welcome\nplease click the 'help' button to learn more and contact me more easily."
MESSAGE2="Hello,\nI am a Telegram bot that you can control and use to purchase our online products."
MESSAGE3="You can control and use me by sending these commands:\n/order - explore the store and our products.\n/myorders - view your order history.\n/myactiveorder - view your active order.\n/deleteorder - you can use this order to delete your order, but the order you want to delete must meet the cancellation conditions.\nOtherwise, unfortunately, your order can't be canceled.\n/callrequest - for phone contact with the store.\n/admin - using this command, you can be approved as an admin and operate."
ADMIN_START_MESSAGE="Dear admin, you have all permissions and access to me and user information, and you can use these commands to access the features.\n\nservices:\n/order - explore the store and our products.\n/myorders - view your order history.\n/myactiveorder - view your active order.\n/deleteorder - you can use this order to delete your order, but the order you want to delete must meet the cancellation conditions.\nOtherwise, unfortunately, your order can't be canceled.\n\nCRUD operations:\n/crud - using this command, you can perform CRUD operations."